---
import FlowLayout from "../layouts/FlowLayout.astro";
---

<FlowLayout
  title="About – Ahmad Madi"
  step={2}
  total={5}
  backHref="/"
  nextHref="/work"
>
  <section class="space-y-6">
    <header class="space-y-2">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">About me</h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        Senior Software Engineer with strong experience building and operating
        cloud-based systems in production environments.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 p-4 space-y-3">
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">
        I have over five years of experience working on internal platforms,
        backend services, and operational tooling where reliability and
        performance are critical.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">
        My work focuses on designing scalable backend systems, automating
        workflows using cloud-native architectures, and modernizing legacy
        systems without disrupting production.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 p-4">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-200">
          What I do best
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-300">
          <li>• Designing scalable backend APIs and services</li>
          <li>• Cloud automation using AWS and event-driven systems</li>
          <li>• Improving production performance and stability</li>
          <li>• Migrating legacy systems to modern stacks</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 p-4">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-200">
          How I work
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-300">
          <li>• Pragmatic and impact-driven</li>
          <li>• Strong ownership from design to rollout</li>
          <li>• Clear communication of tradeoffs</li>
          <li>• Focused on shipping and iterating safely</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 p-4">
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-200">
        Currently
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">
        Working remotely at Washmen on internal platforms, operational analytics,
        and cloud automation systems. Also building independent projects such as
        MenuCraft.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</FlowLayout>
